//           "content_html" : "\n<p>Serenity Caldwell:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>More than anything else, the Apple Pencil is the game changer for\nthe 2018 iPad. So I used it to draw, write, and create a review\ndone entirely on the 9.7-inch tablet.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>Very impressive video. She even composed her own score in GarageBand.</p>\n\n<p style=\"padding-top: 1.5em;\"><em>Link: <strong><a href=\"https://www.imore.com/my-97-ipad-2018-review-drawn-written-edited-and-produced-ipad\">imore.com/my-97-ipad-2018-review-drawn-written-edited-and…</a></strong></em></p>\n"
